Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.70,0:00:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說阿和呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.04,0:00:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.90,0:00:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟阿和開始交往時的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.91,0:00:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.91,0:00:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.15,0:00:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然把你找來這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.75,0:00:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.12,0:00:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去雖然沒有跟你同班過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都很注意和也同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.76,0:00:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然聽到這種話\N任誰都會呆住的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是\N我想至少要告訴你我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.33,0:00:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你聽我說!掰掰!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.34,0:00:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.85,0:00:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…像我這種…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.85,0:00:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不，不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.62,0:00:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.99,0:01:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.39,0:01:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在明天的創立祭上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要告訴阿和…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.97,0:01:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.30,0:01:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直說不出口的事情…


